{"tid":368445,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"做得好朋友就唔好因為一啲小事而唔再聯絡","createTime":"2017-08-21T14:19:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-21T15:17:22.000Z","uid":22488,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c3d16cd3d9bd9b76154935d111ac3b89c43eedc4","tid":368445,"uid":22488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T14:19:35.000Z","msg":"人愈大愈難識朋友<br />\n做得好朋友都稱得上係一種緣分<br />\n個天比得呢種緣分你同你既好朋友<br />\n就應該好好珍惜<br />\n千萬唔好因為好小既事而遠離個班曾經一齊癲過喪過既死黨<br />\n<br />\n可能有時朋友既行為會令你覺得不討好<br />\n但係諗深一層<br />\n其實你地都曾經經歷過唔少既事<br />\n係咪因為某次發生既事而斷絕呢段關係?<br />\n<br />\n朋友應該坦誠相對<br />\n覺得相處得唔舒服就三口六面講清楚<br />\n人與人相處少不免有磨擦<br />\n最重要既係互相體諒<br />\n但唔係自己話反面就反面<br />\n咁樣對班朋友一啲都唔尊重<br />\n<br />\n如果你最近同朋友有磨擦既<br />\n快啲搵返人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔好因為面子唔主動出聲<br />\n最緊要係keep到段友誼呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n錯過左就成世啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd54324fc495e9b1c5ab1fe36814f7ae42955efc","tid":368445,"uid":22488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T14:26:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db60944e51ee71fe4a654a37c4f0baf29f553c41","tid":368445,"uid":11447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T14:28:06.000Z","msg":"樓主做乜改名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76d73b38bf08feb8f7fa3dd810b0f99b0a138c51","tid":368445,"uid":22488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T14:29:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主做乜改名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好驚自爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ed971074b802259c3e11c68360f46e917e3f78b","tid":368445,"uid":24570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T14:30:10.000Z","msg":"agree<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=